                "invention-title": [
                    "Fuel cell system, light load equipment and control method",
                    "燃料电池系统、轻载设备及控制方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the field of fuel cells, and provides a fuel cell system, light-load equipment and a control method, and the fuel cell system comprises a hydrogen supply mechanism used for supplying hydrogen to a fuel cell stack; a discharge port of the fuel cell stack is used for discharging excessive hydrogen and water generated by the fuel cell stack, the water generated by the fuel cell stack is introduced into the hydrogen production mechanism to produce hydrogen, and an outlet of the hydrogen production mechanism is connected with the hydrogen supply mechanism. The fuel cell is used for solving the problems of waste caused by incomplete utilization of hydrogen and waste of produced water in the working process of the fuel cell in the prior art. According to the fuel cell system provided by the invention, the hydrogen production mechanism is arranged between the fuel cell stack and the hydrogen supply mechanism, unreacted hydrogen is recovered, the hydrogen production mechanism uses water generated by the fuel cell stack to produce hydrogen, and the hydrogen is supplied to the fuel cell stack again, so that effective utilization of the generated water is realized, and hydrolysis hydrogen production is more convenient while being used; and the energy utilization efficiency of the system and the gain of the fuel cell system are improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及燃料电池领域，提供一种燃料电池系统、轻载设备及控制方法，其中，一种燃料电池系统，包括：供氢机构用于给燃料电池堆供氢气；燃料电池堆的排放口用于排出过剩氢气和燃料电池堆产生的水，燃料电池堆产生的水通入制氢机构中制取氢气，制氢机构的出口与供氢机构连接。用以解决现有技术中燃料电池工作过程中氢气利用不完全导致的浪费并对生产的水浪费的问题。本发明提供的燃料电池系统，通过在燃料电池堆与供氢机构之间设置制氢机构，回收未反应的氢气，制氢机构利用燃料电池堆产生的水制得氢气，重新供给燃料电池堆，实现对生成水的有效利用，水解制氢随用随制更加便捷，提高了系统的能源利用效率和燃料电池系统的增益。"
                }
            ]
